                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18221023-40-off217 t18221023-40-cd218"></join>, and stealing one gown, value 3 s.; one towel, value 1 d.; one petticoat, value 3 d.; three waiters, value 3 d., and two mugs, value 6 d., her property; and one gown, value 18 d.; one shift, value 6 d., and one pair of stockings, value 1 d.
